net.proteusframework.cms.component.generator

Class MIWTRenderer<T extends PageElement>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.cms.component.generator.MIWTRenderer<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type. Usually a MIWTBean, but may not be in the case of that this is used as a renderer - not a generator.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    DelegateRenderer<T>, Renderer<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MIWTGenerator

    public class MIWTRenderer<T extends PageElement>
extends Object
implements DelegateRenderer<T>
    Renderer for MIWT components.

    If used as a delegate renderer, set the delegate ID.

    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com), Pat Double (double@i2rd.com)
